{"tid":31180,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"學過、自學日文巴絲入一入","createTime":"2016-12-09T13:51:14.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-09T21:07:34.000Z","uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2a031fc061abfe164f4d3ceced5ddabdefd63fc3","tid":31180,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T13:51:14.000Z","msg":"小小才剛開始記五十音 有啲好低能嘅問題想問<br />\n如果你未聽過個字點讀 你點樣分個字嘅聲道？姐係第一聲 第二聲個啲高低音<br />\n求指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4c2cadeab49529045e50e6875dbacb9de389af3","tid":31180,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T13:51:24.000Z","msg":"小弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d77114dcec746337e8aa67acef8dae8872f0a63","tid":31180,"uid":22894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T14:35:59.000Z","msg":"日文得高低音之分，唔似廣東話分九聲<br />\n<br />\n如果你學東京腔日語，第一粒音一定同第二粒音高低音不同，但係點讀係要死記"},{"pid":"e854f10e00983354019bd01ab9a80d61c3c7dfd1","tid":31180,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T14:38:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>日文得高低音之分，唔似廣東話分九聲<br />\n<br />\n如果你學東京腔日語，第一粒音一定同第二粒音高低音不同，但係點讀係要死記</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n東京腔語姐係常用語？"},{"pid":"781d208e3ae6b2c86cf8335f65e8b070e8610f41","tid":31180,"uid":21064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T14:49:00.000Z","msg":"市面有好多教科書 入面有碟教你點讀每課既生字 有哂高底位<br />\n唔想用錢既就去試管到 都有好多教學俾你入門 <br />\n無話邊個腔係常用語既 因為唔同地方個發聲都唔同<br />\n關東同關西個腔都唔同 <br />\n你識講個字 個文法岩人地就明 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">不過你都係記左五十音先</span>"},{"pid":"4a92faffca395715c6d9021b86ed5ea1f8da86de","tid":31180,"uid":47303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T20:17:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/30628/page/1?ref=android\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/30628/page/1?ref=android</a><br />\n學乜日文呀 你咁弱智 學咩都唔識架啦"},{"pid":"f868170a8650c00924ecab1d5759db844e1e1256","tid":31180,"uid":43202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T20:45:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/30628/page/1?ref=android\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/30628/page/1?ref=android</a><br />\n學乜日文呀 你咁弱智 學咩都唔識架啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n原來係5190 on9仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 心諗做乜無啦啦屌人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"319e96a8b1bb9ca0f19fd07ad97a6cccc4075861","tid":31180,"uid":47303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T20:57:45.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"d8cc2011a47284d6cc0142c3f6879e59de7080c4","tid":31180,"uid":47303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T21:01:19.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"df11003a25dc33773ad9a8032ef84a20d0fef096","tid":31180,"uid":43483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T21:07:34.000Z","msg":"買本日文字典咪有寫應該用咩音讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/3s5n4hcx\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F3s5n4hcx&h=3145affc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/lbt1z3he\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Flbt1z3he&h=f05ed2a5&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}